trans-unit.source: This is a Web application developed in the context of the research project Processing and cataloging of a written corpus in ELE produced by Chinese students, ECCOTEELE (FFI2016-80280-R) coordinated from Universitat de Lleida.
The aim of this application is to facilitate developing and cataloging a corpus of texts produced by Chinese University students of Spanish as a foreign language (ELE).
Client: Angular application consuming server API.
Server: Spring Boot application providing REST API.
Project coordination: Mª Ángeles Calero Fernández (macalero@filcef.udl.cat)
Spanish Government, Ministry of Science, Innovation and Universities
European Union, European Regional Development Fund
